OL,3,CNewquay's minor injury unit 'could cut
OL,4,Copening hours' amid staffing crisis
OL,6,FNewquay's minor injuries unit is
OL,7,Fexperiencing a staffing crisis and
OL,8,Fcould be set to further reduce its
OL,9,Fopening hours, sparking anger and
OL,10,Fconfusion among patients.
OL,12,FITV West Country understands the
OL,13,Fcentre, based at the town's community
OL,14,Fhospital, is short of nurses ahead of
OL,15,Fthe summer months, when the town's
OL,16,Fpopulation swells to around 100,000.
OL,18,FPhillipa Mitchell, who lives in Porth,
OL,19,Fsuffered a leg injury last weekend and
OL,20,Fattended the MIU.
