OL,3,CNewquay's minor injury unit 'could cut
OL,4,Copening hours' amid staffing crisis
OL,6,F"I was treated by the lovely staff who
OL,7,Fwere all looking a bit disgruntled and
OL,8,Fchatting amongst themselves," she
OL,9,Fsaid. "They were distraught, they
OL,10,Fhaven't got enough staff there, they
OL,11,Fare stressing at the moment."JIt was
OL,12,Frevealed that the unit is in the
OL,13,Fmiddle of a staffing crisis. Two
OL,14,Fmonths ago, its opening hours were
OL,15,Freduced to five days a week, and there
OL,16,Fare rumours that could be cut even
OL,17,Ffurther.J"The community hospital and
OL,18,Fthe staff are just amazing," Phillipa
OL,19,Fsaid.
