OL,3,CNewquay's minor injury unit 'could cut
OL,4,Copening hours' amid staffing crisis
OL,6,F"You couldn't want for a better minor
OL,7,Finjuries unit. The thought of having
OL,8,Fto go to Treliske and sit in a queue
OL,9,Ffor five hours, which isn't unheard
OL,10,Fof, is shocking."
OL,12,FAt the height of summer, the
OL,13,Fpopulation of Newquay grows from
OL,14,F22,000 to around 100,000. Phillipa
OL,15,Fsays the county's health service
OL,16,Fstruggles to manage the influx at the
OL,17,Fbest of times.J"We are a holiday
OL,18,Fdestination, a growing community, more
OL,19,Fand more houses being built, and
OL,20,Fweekends are the busiest times," she
OL,21,Fsaid.
