OL,3,CNewquay's minor injury unit 'could cut
OL,4,Copening hours' amid staffing crisis
OL,6,F"Treliske is chock-a-block, they keep
OL,7,Ftelling us 'don't come here unless
OL,8,Fit's a real emergency.' So what will
OL,9,Fhappen in the summer? Particularly
OL,10,FAugust, we've got Boardmasters
OL,11,F(Festival) just up the road. I dread
OL,12,Fto think what's going to happen."JA
OL,13,Fspokesman for Cornwall Partnership NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust said: "In March 2024,
OL,15,Fwe amended the opening hours of
OL,16,FNewquay Minor Injury Unit to 8am to
OL,17,F8pm, Fridays to Tuesdays. This
OL,18,Ftemporary change was made to support
OL,19,Four staff and ensure safe patient
OL,20,Fcare. It reflects the times when the
OL,21,Funit is busier and remains in place.
