OL,3,CNewquay's minor injury unit 'could cut
OL,4,Copening hours' amid staffing crisis
OL,6,F"However, we are still experiencing
OL,7,Fstaffing challenges due to vacancies
OL,8,Fand staff sickness. These have led to
OL,9,Fsome short-term changes to the
OL,10,Favailability of the minor injury unit
OL,11,Fin recent weeks, including early
OL,12,Fclosing or late opening times.
OL,14,F"In line with our operating policies,
OL,15,Fopening hours remain under constant
OL,16,Freview and we allocate resources
OL,17,Facross the county in order to keep our
OL,18,Fbusiest units open and safely able to
OL,19,Ftreat as many people as possible.
